<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个精灵很庞大！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他发光的秃头都碰到了天花板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑色的卷卷的胡子遮住了他半个脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他棕色的手臂、胸膛和肩膀都有大块的肌肉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>精灵穿着黑色丝绸的裤子，带着很大的金耳环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是谁？”泽巴大声说，“他从哪里来的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个精灵！”阿拉丁靠向他的妈妈说，“他是从那个灯里出来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快让他走！”泽巴恳求道，“我很害怕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是神灯里的精灵！”精灵把双手交叉在他的大大的赤裸的胸前说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要把我送走。我是你的奴隶，我会为你们服务。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不需要奴隶。”泽巴说，她的身体因为害怕而发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转向她的儿子:“求求你快让他走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁把灯从妈妈的手上抢了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要听我妈妈的，神灯精灵。”阿拉丁命令道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都很饿！给我们拿一些国王吃的东西来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>精灵消失了！但是一眨眼的工夫，他就回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着一个很大的银盘，上面有六个装满食物的金盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把盘子放在地毯上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好丰盛啊！”阿拉丁忍不住大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有牛肉和羊肉做的香肠。有一盘甜菜沙拉和白萝卜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其它的盘子里装着米饭和豆，橄榄，坚果，还有奶酪馅饼，闻起来太香了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，呼地一声，精灵消失了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，快来！”阿拉丁开心地喊道，“多么丰盛啊，快来吃吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！”泽巴回答说，“我不会吃的。那个可恶的精灵吓到我了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来和我一起坐。”他拍了拍旁边的地毯笑着说，“开心地吃吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴终于放弃。她坐下来，拿了一块奶酪馅饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从来没有吃过这样的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它真的是国王餐桌上的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我，儿子。”泽巴给阿拉丁倒了一杯咖啡说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是这个精灵把你从宝库里救出来的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，不是。”阿拉丁回答道，“是那个戒指精灵把我救出去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他长得很好笑，妈妈，而且很矮。他的帽子上有铃铛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁想起那个小小的棕色的精灵，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得神灯精灵是不同种类的精灵。”他补充道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”阿拉丁的妈妈说，“他想把我吓死！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她靠向阿拉丁，悄悄说:“儿子，你要把那盏灯扔了，还有那个戒指。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们只会给我们带来麻烦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，妈妈。”阿拉丁说，“我们很幸运，应该接受这个事实。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想想吧，马格里布走了这么远的路就是为了找这个灯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他只想要宝库里的这一个东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以它一定很重要，我们一定要留着这个灯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有那个戒指？”泽巴说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。”阿拉丁说，“如果没有那个戒指，我应该还被活埋在地下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也不可能再看到我了。我永远都不会把这个戒指摘下来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的妈妈叹了口气，摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想怎么样就怎么样吧。”她说，“但是我不想再看到那个可恶的精灵了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>